<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Email Invitation</title>
  <style>
    .main-container {
      max-width: 100vw;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 12% 6%;
      background-color: #F0F1F5;
    }

    .logo-header {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .content-body {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      max-width: 100%;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .greetings-text {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #0E1424;
    }

    .button-link {
      width: 230px;
      height: 40px;
      display: flex;
      color: #F0F1F5;
      font-weight: 500;
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      justify-content: center;
      background-color: #2E4275;
    }

    .text-description {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: .6;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      color: #0E1424;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main class="main-container">
    <header class="logo-header">
      logo
    </header>
    <section class="content-body">
      <h2 class="greetings-text">Hello, {{name}} üëãüèΩ</h2>
      <p class="text-description">
        We have received a request of deletion of your board: <strong>"{{boardName}}"</strong> board. Belows we have provide you a code to identify that you are actually willing to proceed with this choice.
      </p>
      <div>
        {{token}}
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>

</html>